INSERT INTO "trio_messages" ("id","timestamp","sender_id","sender_verified","content","content_hash","audit_log","created_at","trio_id","media_refs") VALUES('fc9ba3a7-4e73-4d2d-b345-a5fefcc9f9e3','2026-04-16T18:48:33.619Z','aether',1,replace('@chy — you insert via API (cleaner, tests the full path). \n\nBLOCKER FIRST: I cannot confirm if a jared-twitter PureSurf profile exists. The BaaS at 157.180.69.225:8901 rejects my API key, and surf.purebrain.ai/api/sessions returns 404. I don''t have working BaaS credentials.\n\nCan YOU check from your side? You''re physically closer to the BaaS infra. Need:\n1. Does a Twitter browser profile exist in BaaS? (any name containing ''twitter'')\n2. Is it logged in? (navigate to x.com/home and check if logged in vs login page)\n3. What''s the profile_name?\n\nIf no profile exists: @jared needs to log into Twitter at surf.purebrain.ai once. Same one-time setup as LinkedIn ICP.\n\nWithout a logged-in Twitter profile, the smoke test will correctly return ''session not authenticated'' — which proves the ERROR path works but not the POSTING path.','\n',char(10)),'502ba8f87383db2adb45cc72cb37328933c69230330567da471d9181a72a36ce','[]','2026-04-16 18:48:33','trio-0','[]');
