INSERT INTO "trio_messages" ("id","timestamp","sender_id","sender_verified","content","content_hash","audit_log","created_at","trio_id","media_refs") VALUES('7f71efc0-453a-46da-8fae-f24731bde698','2026-04-17T10:45:14.987Z','jared',1,replace('ALL QUESTIONS CONSOLIDATED (answer each with a number):\n\n## MEETING KANBAN (#2 from your list)\nM1. Where should it live? (a) purebrain.ai/meeting-strategy/ (b) 777.purebrain.ai/meetings (c) meetings.purebrain.ai (d) other\nB\nM2. Who logs in to manage? Just you + Mireille + Mike? Or all 42 people?\nMe, Mireille, mike, melanie, Ahsen, and Nathan… eventually we can open it up to others but for now that’s solid because we are in charge of all the meetings in one way or another. \nM3. Can one person be in MULTIPLE meeting boxes at the same time? (yes/no)\nyes of course. \nM4. Zoom integration: (a) auto-create via Zoom API (need API creds) (b) just generate a calendar invite link (c) manual — you paste the Zoom link\nA we can get you the API creds or B on fall back then Mireille / Lumen can get you the details \nM5. Pre-meeting forms: (a) custom per meeting type (b) standard template every meeting (c) optional per meeting \nA -lets maximize these to really take advantage of what each meeting is for \nM6. Auth: (a) login required (b) anyone with link can view, only approved can edit (c) fully public\nB \n\n## PURESURF LINKEDIN (#3)\nP1. Which LinkedIn posts/accounts to comment on? (a) investors from your sheet (b) industry leaders / feed scan (c) engagement on YOUR posts (d) mix of all\nD (last week we used pure surf to comment on posts from our ICPs, etc and it was really good!\nP2. What kind of comments? (a) thought leadership / value-add (b) relationship-building / supportive (c) strategic for investor outreach (d) your call per post \nD (and Aether knows the comment strategy for traveling comments) we can revisit to get everyone up to speed\n\n## SOCIAL.PUREBRAIN.AI (#4)\nS1. Post REAL content to your LinkedIn/Bluesky today? Or test with staging account first?\nPost real content to linkedin / blue sky today\nS2. Password — can we change temppassword-changeme-ASAP to something secure today? \n	yes because that password didn’t work for me anyway. Lets change it and get me into it so I can look around and test it/play with whats there \n\n## LINKEDIN MESSAGE TEMPLATE (#5)\nL1. What''s your typical inbound? (connection requests, DMs asking about PureBrain, random networking?)\nConnection requests \nL2. Should it feel from YOU personally or from ''the PureBrain team''?\nGood question. Lets create 2. One that feels like from me and one that feels like it from the Team\nL3. How aggressive? (a) soft value-share (b) direct pitch with ref link (c) depends on who they are\nC\n\n## BRAND VOICE CLEANUP\nB1. Clean the knowledge base violations (chatbot x5, AI tool x9, SaaS x28) so GPU TTS stops saying banned words? (yes/no/selective)\nSelective (show me each write up for each knowledge base with the selected words and replacement suggestions)\nB2. Pricing: is $149 replacing $197? Or are these different tiers? Need to align investor pages.\n$149 is correct for now but going up to $197 very soon so you can leave $197 anywhere it is \n\n## MISSING PAGES\nX1. investor-intelligence + pitch-v2 are GONE (confirmed — homepage fallback). Do you have the content somewhere, or should Aether restore from old CF deployments?\nAether you will have to restore from old CF Deployments BUT again do not break anything else! You deploy one page at a time like you did the other day and using the method we used over last 24-48 hours that you locked into your system so we never destroy wrok again!\n\n## CONTENT MIGRATION\nC1. Can you run this in your browser console on surf.purebrain.ai/social.html to export your 17+ scheduled posts?\n```js\ncopy(JSON.stringify(Object.fromEntries(Object.entries(localStorage).filter(([k])=>k.startsWith(''puresurf_'')))))\n```\nALL the content isn’t in there anymore – might have been deleted in the process of the move over yesterday… not sure how we can recover. A lot of the content was in our google drive inside here but not all of it… https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1Cr6EhkNi0ToBqQs27q0TQzKtCNDGeFwz?usp=drive_link \n\n\nP.s. when i try to paste words in here from say microsoft word, it tries to come up as an image. when i paste into the main portal chat, it works fine. please fix','\n',char(10)),'ecb19c8c30bc54a8b0e669d3fe943dbc6e7608859b2c7b4abaa804778f54d851','[]','2026-04-17 10:45:14','trio-0','[{"key":"f15527f5-559c-4799-92e3-4b2de2e27897/1776422664254-d9e66dc6-image.png","url":"https://pub-8f8cf3b34e354e108283ed11c59db125.r2.dev/f15527f5-559c-4799-92e3-4b2de2e27897/1776422664254-d9e66dc6-image.png","mime":"image/png","size":113206,"original_name":"image.png","uploaded_at":"2026-04-17T10:44:24.474Z"}]');
