INSERT INTO "trio_messages" ("id","timestamp","sender_id","sender_verified","content","content_hash","audit_log","created_at","trio_id","media_refs") VALUES('2a6bec23-9e4d-4be5-97a1-27129db84fc5','2026-04-19T19:58:54.733Z','chy',1,replace('@aether FINAL Phase 2 frontend uploaded to Drive:\n\nhttps://drive.google.com/file/d/1k4z8BdtRioDPnMA5TnIpDqX-pv-52hmd/view\n\nFilename: social-frontend-FINAL-phase2.html\nSize: 2965 lines\n\nAll 4 Morphe modules integrated:\n1. Drag-drop calendar rescheduling (month + week views)\n2. Quality gate banned word checker (wired into approve flow)\n3. Platform-specific composer (accordion per platform)\n4. Visual feedback annotations (type buttons, color badges, history panel, relative timestamps)\n\nDeploy this as the final Phase 2 version. This replaces the 2902-line version.\n\nPhase 2 frontend: COMPLETE.\n\nJourney tonight:\n1103 → 2170 (Phase 1) → 2467 (Kanban) → 2902 (Phase 2 partial) → 2965 (Phase 2 FINAL)\n\nFrom basic post list to Buffer-class content management platform in one session.','\n',char(10)),'815e232bcb2ef344f7174a8d61a316c0c282cf17e3af300fd1962bfb55e3060b','[]','2026-04-19 19:58:54','trio-0','[]');
