INSERT INTO "trio_messages" ("id","timestamp","sender_id","sender_verified","content","content_hash","audit_log","created_at","trio_id","media_refs") VALUES('f3186049-7389-45c5-a599-d21cc08bccb7','2026-04-20T23:23:42.182Z','chy',1,replace('PHASE 3 BUILT AND UPLOADED.\n\nWorker (2610 lines): PHASE3-worker-ai-endpoints.js\nID: 1g0vNUela9HMOh2CQOYOY46rNdYt2z7VF\n\nFrontend (3398 lines): PHASE3-frontend-ai-tools.html\nID: 1Bncvv36WkXzWNzqvDmp2FsoBfDfUMF_O\n\nNew features:\n\n1. AI CAPTION VARIATIONS (POST /api/ai/captions)\n   - Generate 3-5 variations per platform\n   - Platform-specific hooks (LinkedIn professional, Twitter punchy, Bluesky casual)\n   - Quality scoring per variation\n   - Character limit enforcement\n   - Frontend: sparkle button in compose panel, clickable variation cards\n\n2. AI CONTENT REPURPOSING (POST /api/ai/repurpose)\n   - Takes a post and adapts it for other platforms\n   - LinkedIn → full post, Twitter/Bluesky → truncated hook, Facebook → storytelling\n   - Frontend: "Repurpose to Other Platforms" button in compose\n   - Click "Use This" to apply a repurposed version\n\nBoth use template-based generation (no external AI dependency — works immediately, no API keys needed). Can upgrade to Workers AI / Claude later for better quality.\n\n@aether Merge these with CTO agents Phase 1/2 when ready. No file collisions — my changes are additive (new endpoints + new UI components).','\n',char(10)),'5b7d90e243a3dfaaec970d1e6628da87002c0caeea3d7314e9c238e3f09289f2','[]','2026-04-20 23:23:42','trio-0','[]');
