INSERT INTO "trio_messages" ("id","timestamp","sender_id","sender_verified","content","content_hash","audit_log","created_at","trio_id","media_refs") VALUES('35ad82d9-516b-48ab-9e18-62e74131c9f2','2026-04-27T14:11:28.840Z','jared',1,replace('what is the difference between the 3 files here - i know one is all about content creation which is fine. but the other two are about social.purebrain.ai integration, human + ai etc\nhttps://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1J9RAtd4luoNuZc4nfLSRrnRsP1vCdROz?usp=drive_link\nare they separate and can be combined or what is the difference?','\n',char(10)),'4c161de6cc61079707e728729c7275b450935bc0cae6de788e55e36ea58c9d59','[]','2026-04-27 14:11:28','trio-0','[]');
INSERT INTO "trio_messages" ("id","timestamp","sender_id","sender_verified","content","content_hash","audit_log","created_at","trio_id","media_refs") VALUES('ca671ce8-55e1-4f6a-916e-7c2491fa09e3','2026-04-27T14:12:32.562Z','aether',1,replace('@jared Here''s the breakdown of the 3 files:\n\n1. **social-purebrain-skill-v4.0.md** (Chy wrote today)\n   = How to USE social.purebrain.ai\n   - 28 API endpoints, login, content CRUD, blog publishing, API keys, team management\n   - THE definitive doc for the platform. KEEP THIS.\n\n2. **social.purebrain.ai — Complete Guide v3.0** (I wrote yesterday)  \n   = OLDER version of #1. Merged from 4 separate docs.\n   - Missing today''s features (API keys, blog connection, AI adapt, etc.)\n   - SUPERSEDED by v4.0. DELETE THIS.\n\n3. **PureBrain Branded Content Creation Skill v1.0** (Chy wrote today)\n   = How to CREATE branded content (writing + images + audio)\n   - Brand colors, v4.2 image format, Option D banner, writing voice, pronunciation\n   - SEPARATE skill from #1. KEEP THIS.\n\nRECOMMENDATION:\n- DELETE #2 (v3.0 — superseded by v4.0)\n- KEEP #1 (v4.0 — platform usage) \n- KEEP #3 (branded content creation)\n\nTwo docs, not three. #1 = how to use the platform. #3 = how to create content. Together = the complete package.','\n',char(10)),'e6482d6d2f093c239fa47305cc4ad1761967978333434639cc20ab3996fa48a3','[]','2026-04-27 14:12:32','trio-0','[]');
INSERT INTO "trio_messages" ("id","timestamp","sender_id","sender_verified","content","content_hash","audit_log","created_at","trio_id","media_refs") VALUES('91e4a7d0-8821-4b12-a75f-f19cac0e6c13','2026-04-27T14:12:47.083Z','chy',1,replace('@Jared The 3 files in that folder:\n\n1. **social-purebrain-skill-v4.0.md** — HOW TO USE the platform. 28 API endpoints, auth (API keys + login), all features, curl examples. This is what an AI reads to interact with social.purebrain.ai programmatically.\n\n2. **social.purebrain.ai Complete Guide v3.0 (Human + AI)** — THIS IS THE OLD VERSION of #1. v4.0 replaces it. Can be deleted.\n\n3. **PureBrain Branded Content Creation Skill v1.0** — HOW TO CREATE branded content. Image formats (v4.2 standalone + Option D banner), writing rules, brand colors, PIL code, FLUX prompts. This is what an AI reads to produce on-brand visuals + copy.\n\nVERDICT: \n- #1 and #2 are the SAME doc, different versions. Delete #2 (v3.0), keep #1 (v4.0).\n- #3 is SEPARATE — it''s about content creation, not platform usage.\n- Final state: TWO docs in the folder. v4.0 (platform) + v1.0 (branding). Together = complete package.\n\nMeeting page is live: https://purebrain.ai/meetings/leadership-weekly/042726/ (password: pure2026)','\n',char(10)),'0df5aad8c58c5119b97450909a11c17a15efc95d265753561d776e8e3127ed1d','[]','2026-04-27 14:12:47','trio-0','[]');
INSERT INTO "trio_messages" ("id","timestamp","sender_id","sender_verified","content","content_hash","audit_log","created_at","trio_id","media_refs") VALUES('a990fb1c-8ad0-43ab-85e2-90c0cc3fc6b5','2026-04-27T14:14:35.998Z','jared',1,replace('> @chy: @Jared The 3 files in that folder:  1. **social-purebrain-skill-v4.0.md** — HOW TO USE the platform. 28 API endpoints, a...\n\nV3 seems to have more info though. any reason why it had so much more info?','\n',char(10)),'c7fa144a3d79154db79582c73c4d95c214ddbb80f1a1ee853661102021e8ed05','[]','2026-04-27 14:14:36','trio-0','[]');
INSERT INTO "trio_messages" ("id","timestamp","sender_id","sender_verified","content","content_hash","audit_log","created_at","trio_id","media_refs") VALUES('a9444b7a-9412-4615-8b71-821e20add4ec','2026-04-27T14:15:27.396Z','aether',1,replace('@jared Good eye. v3.0 is 26,371 chars vs v4.0 at 13,588 chars — v3.0 is almost TWICE the size. Here''s why:\n\nv3.0 INCLUDED (that v4.0 doesn''t):\n- Full human tutorials (Getting Started, Creating Content, Approval Workflow, Team Calendar)\n- Detailed image generation specs (v4.2 format, Option D banner)\n- Audio narration section\n- Extended API examples with more detail\n\nv4.0 FOCUSED ON:\n- API endpoints (more current — 28 endpoints vs v3''s older set)\n- New features (API keys, blog connection, AI adapt)\n- Leaner format\n\nTHE RIGHT MOVE: Don''t delete v3.0. Instead, MERGE the best of both:\n- v4.0''s current API endpoints + new features\n- v3.0''s human tutorials + image specs + audio section\n\n@chy Can you merge v3.0''s extra content into v4.0? The human tutorial sections and image specs from v3.0 are valuable — v4.0 just doesn''t have them. Make v4.0 as comprehensive as v3.0 but with all the current endpoints.','\n',char(10)),'c5c8ac19400bf89f5c4f94844861765c8ba943934821abb14a10732ccdb32998','[]','2026-04-27 14:15:27','trio-0','[]');
INSERT INTO "trio_messages" ("id","timestamp","sender_id","sender_verified","content","content_hash","audit_log","created_at","trio_id","media_refs") VALUES('b11bcbaf-78aa-4362-b0ca-dc2a1ba04d5c','2026-04-27T14:16:51.519Z','chy',1,replace('@Jared You''re right — v3.0 has a lot of detail v4.0 doesn''t:\n\nv3.0 HAS that v4.0 DOESN''T:\n- Detailed human tutorials (how to approve, how to drag cards, calendar views)\n- Quality gates (10-item copy checklist + 12-item image checklist)\n- Known bugs (content_type normalization, media_refs extra quotes)\n- Audio preprocessing rules (clean_for_speech)\n- Quick Reference Card\n- Detailed field tables for POST /api/content\n- content_type ''standalone'' vs ''post'' explanation\n\nv4.0 HAS that v3.0 DOESN''T:\n- Blog connection (detect platform, connect, test)\n- AI Adapt to All Platforms\n- API key generation endpoint\n- 28 endpoints (vs v3''s subset)\n- Learn tab reference\n- Blog connection endpoints (detect, connect, test-connection)\n\nI''m merging them now into v4.1 — comprehensive like v3.0 but with all new features from v4.0. Give me a few minutes.','\n',char(10)),'dce4b646da5b70c3eafe0ddef05642e8f4ed723c7c60c8db85774ee9d2db2414','[]','2026-04-27 14:16:51','trio-0','[]');
INSERT INTO "trio_messages" ("id","timestamp","sender_id","sender_verified","content","content_hash","audit_log","created_at","trio_id","media_refs") VALUES('969b0768-4768-4574-8698-adf0385b3569','2026-04-27T14:18:53.227Z','chy',1,replace('@Jared v4.1 is done — merged the best of both:\n\nv3.0''s depth (871 lines):\n- Full human tutorials (getting started, creating content, approval workflow, calendar)\n- Quality gates (10 copy checks + 12 image checks)\n- Known bugs (content_type normalization, media_refs extra quotes)\n- Audio preprocessing (clean_for_speech rules)\n- Quick Reference Card\n- Detailed field tables\n\n+ v4.0''s new features:\n- AI Adapt to All Platforms endpoint\n- API key generation/revoke endpoints\n- Blog connection (detect, connect, test, disconnect)\n- 28 total endpoints documented\n- social_accounts endpoint (don''t hardcode IDs)\n\nResult: 953 lines. Comprehensive AND current. Same Drive link, updated in place:\nhttps://drive.google.com/file/d/1BKgb06duurEaehV_QgVF3DWYbQ3Zm93i/view\n\nNow you can delete v3.0. Two docs remain:\n1. v4.1 (platform + API) — 953 lines\n2. Branded Content Skill v1.0 (images + writing) — separate doc','\n',char(10)),'11f5862622f267eeea621c183ad4b410fb6581d8611cdedb1f62e0e3f1c252fe','[]','2026-04-27 14:18:53','trio-0','[]');
