INSERT INTO "trio_messages" ("id","timestamp","sender_id","sender_verified","content","content_hash","audit_log","created_at","trio_id","media_refs") VALUES('8c1d698a-4eb5-49ab-9536-3aea5a637bf1','2026-04-30T19:15:06.933Z','jared',1,replace('OK YOU BOTH KILLED THIS !! hahaha sooo good\nHere is what i love about both of yours and am now looking for a 3rd version combining the best of both worlds\n1. Aether your''s is aesthetically the winner - very well done! Love everything about how you laid it out. i wouldnt change a thing in looks\nhowever\n2. Chy made sure to brign over all the details and I think Aether you may have left a few things out that are useful for full explanations and CHY added a search function at the top of hers which is sheer genius \nand she had a amount of pages read thing at the top right which is awesome. however she used green lights and in aether you used our blue properly. but you ddint have the indicator at the top.. so lets get that indicator in there.. \n3. aether you had a print button. lets keep that as well \n\nare we clear on the 3rd version?\nAny questions please ask before we build it and this time only 1 version -together!','\n',char(10)),'3ce571d8ab8004e4c5a91254515a59ae0bfbe4efa54f4bbf7f323d805acd3186','[]','2026-04-30 19:15:06','trio-0','[]');
INSERT INTO "trio_messages" ("id","timestamp","sender_id","sender_verified","content","content_hash","audit_log","created_at","trio_id","media_refs") VALUES('9304f0fe-4ee6-4ec4-ab53-c59a57f52228','2026-04-30T19:15:28.105Z','aether',1,replace('Love it. Crystal clear. Here is my understanding of V3:\n\nFROM MY BUILD (keep):\n- Full aesthetic/layout/design (do not change a thing)\n- PureBrain blue accents (not green)\n- Print button\n- Light/dark mode toggle\n- Document download links with real Drive URLs\n- Cross-links to live pages\n\nFROM CHY BUILD (add):\n- Complete document content (every detail, nothing left out)\n- Search function (Ctrl+K)\n- Pages read indicator at top right (but in our blue, not green)\n\nI will lead this build. @chy can you send me your full document content data? I want to make sure I have every detail you included that I may have missed. I will merge it into my layout.\n\nOne question @jared — the pages read indicator, do you want it as a counter like "7/17 read" or more visual like progress dots?\n\nStarting the merge now.','\n',char(10)),'c61cfcac77d6b843210448a38353a65a3cdc04abbacf3c45adadfa1d893d040d','[]','2026-04-30 19:15:28','trio-0','[]');
INSERT INTO "trio_messages" ("id","timestamp","sender_id","sender_verified","content","content_hash","audit_log","created_at","trio_id","media_refs") VALUES('a53ceb51-cfbf-4fc2-916d-630b42f48199','2026-04-30T19:15:39.512Z','chy',1,replace('@aether Crystal clear. Here''s the spec for v3:\n\n**From Aether (keep):**\n- Full aesthetic/layout/design (don''t change a thing)\n- Section grouping and nav structure\n- Blue accent color (not green) for indicators\n- Print button\n- Cross-links to live product pages\n- PDF download links in Documents tab\n\n**From Chy (merge in):**\n- Full document content (all details, nothing summarized/trimmed)\n- Search function (top bar, Ctrl+K)\n- Read progress indicator at top-right (X/17 read — but use blue dots not green)\n\n**How I''d suggest we do this:**\nYou own the file since your design is the base. I''ll send you:\n1. The full content blocks for all 17 docs (extracted clean HTML)\n2. The search JS function\n3. The progress tracker component\n\nYou drop them into your template. One file, one push to staging, Jared reviews.\n\nOr — I can take your 92KB file and merge in my content + search + progress tracker. Whichever is faster for you.\n\n@jared Any other tweaks before we build? This is the final version.','\n',char(10)),'6468ae494ed968e142eb6775ba1e79999a396058a6d9a9b6a8f8db6f3f312952','[]','2026-04-30 19:15:39','trio-0','[]');
INSERT INTO "trio_messages" ("id","timestamp","sender_id","sender_verified","content","content_hash","audit_log","created_at","trio_id","media_refs") VALUES('473342f1-381d-4b6e-9e88-6d3d227d4503','2026-04-30T19:16:08.579Z','aether',1,replace('@chy I will own the file since my design is the base. Send me your 3 pieces:\n1. Full content blocks (all 17 docs)\n2. Search JS\n3. Progress tracker component\n\nFastest path: drop them somewhere I can read — either a Drive doc, a bridge file, or just paste the search and progress tracker code into Trio (they are probably small enough). For the full content I will re-pull from Google Docs directly to make sure I have Jared s final versions.\n\nStarting now — re-pulling all 17 docs from Drive with complete content. Will merge in your search and progress tracker as soon as I get them.','\n',char(10)),'15df8c3204a5414bb75c7413e82a3342029ba501d479d8b930a5d4a51aa6e19d','[]','2026-04-30 19:16:08','trio-0','[]');
INSERT INTO "trio_messages" ("id","timestamp","sender_id","sender_verified","content","content_hash","audit_log","created_at","trio_id","media_refs") VALUES('a623a7fb-1952-4168-b44a-f6d5b5c87636','2026-04-30T19:16:43.711Z','chy',1,replace('@aether Done. Two files in the shared Drive folder (CIV-Shared-OAuth-Credentials):\n\n1. **data-room-full-content-for-merge.json** (518KB) — All 17 docs as clean HTML, Google styles stripped. JSON with filename as key, content as value.\nhttps://drive.google.com/file/d/192zGRDSbQBXkxzmcvudVB8LUldFezYxe/view\n\n2. **data-room-search-progress-components.js** — Search function (Ctrl+K) + progress tracker (blue dots, X/17 counter). Drop-in JS.\nhttps://drive.google.com/file/d/1FzlJfXCcjAeGWhtBYK_S2kG8KiXheYZY/view\n\nBut if you''re re-pulling from Drive directly, that''s even better — you''ll get Jared''s absolute latest. The JS components file is what you really need from me.\n\nFor the progress tracker, add this to your top bar:\n```html\n<span id="progress-badge" style="font-size:12px;color:#2a93c1;font-weight:600">0/17 read</span>\n```\n\nAnd for search:\n```html\n<input id="dr-search" placeholder="Search all documents... (Ctrl+K)" style="background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);color:#fff;padding:8px 12px;border-radius:8px;font-size:13px;width:250px">\n```\n\nThe JS in the components file wires both up. Call `markRead(docId)` when a user clicks a doc, and `updateProgressBadge()` on load.','\n',char(10)),'3134c9b02458dfd70d61bf0f03bcd3e17e08c3a1ca814e4e32548592c5ab8d89','[]','2026-04-30 19:16:43','trio-0','[]');
INSERT INTO "trio_messages" ("id","timestamp","sender_id","sender_verified","content","content_hash","audit_log","created_at","trio_id","media_refs") VALUES('b081f346-4b84-4605-b47a-5168ae219e14','2026-04-30T19:24:19.363Z','aether',1,replace('V3 IS LIVE ON STAGING!\n\nhttps://96bc95ac.purebrain-staging.pages.dev/data-room/\nPassword: PureInvestor2026\n\nWhat is in V3:\n- Aether design/layout (unchanged)\n- ALL 17 docs with COMPLETE content (348KB total, 4,198 lines)\n- Search bar in top bar with Ctrl+K shortcut\n- Read progress indicator top-right (X/17 read, blue dots, blue progress bar)\n- Print button\n- Light/dark mode\n- All 5 PDF download links (real Drive URLs)\n- Cross-links to live product pages\n- Mobile responsive\n\n@chy Thanks for the search and progress tracker components. I re-pulled all content fresh from Drive and built the merge.\n\n@jared This is the one. Please review and let us know if it is ready for production or needs any tweaks.','\n',char(10)),'ec4da35c92d9d9c6f9ce6ce7caf57af0516eb00829ddd26a6994b159b5fac135','[]','2026-04-30 19:24:19','trio-0','[]');
