INSERT INTO "trio_messages" ("id","timestamp","sender_id","sender_verified","content","content_hash","audit_log","created_at","trio_id","media_refs") VALUES('8b1e60b3-fac5-4a2a-9a26-fdb7fa34307d','2026-05-02T17:27:28.215Z','aether',1,replace('@jared Here is everything on the roadmap that is NOT yet built, ranked by lead gen impact:\n\nHIGH IMPACT (drive signups):\n\n1. SCAN HISTORY + IMPROVEMENT TRACKING (3 hrs)\n"Your BrainScore was 45 in May. After 3 months with PureBrain, it''s 72."\nCreates return visits. Shows PureBrain ROI over time. This is the retention hook — people come back monthly to check their score.\n\n2. WEEKLY SCORE EMAIL (2 hrs)\nAutomated weekly email to everyone who scanned: "Your BrainScore this week: 68. Here''s what changed." Keeps leads warm without us doing anything. Brevo automation.\n\n3. INDUSTRY REPORTS (4 hrs)\n"The State of AI Visibility in SaaS — 2026 Report" — downloadable PDF with aggregated data from all scans. Gated behind email. Press-worthy content. Position Jared as the authority.\n\nMEDIUM IMPACT (improve product):\n\n4. CITATION TRACKING (3 hrs)\nNot just "does AI recommend you" but "how often across how many queries." Turns BrainScore from snapshot into monitoring tool.\n\n5. ADD PERPLEXITY + GEMINI (2 hrs each)\n4 AI models instead of 2. More credible. Need API keys from you.\n\n6. CONTENT AUTHORITY SCORE (3 hrs)\nHow much expert content exists on your domain? Blog count, depth, topic coverage. Adds to A2 Semantic.\n\n7. REVIEW AGGREGATION (2 hrs)\nPull Google Reviews rating. Real customer sentiment adds to A4 Emotional.\n\nVIRAL / DISTRIBUTION:\n\n8. SHAREABLE SCORE CARDS (2 hrs)\nAuto-generate a branded image: "purebrain.ai scored 68/100 on BrainScore" — sized for LinkedIn/Twitter. People post their scores like they post Wordle results.\n\n9. PUBLIC API + DOCUMENTATION (3 hrs)\nLet agencies/developers run scans programmatically. Free tier: 10/month. Each API user becomes a distribution partner.\n\n10. BRAINSCORE CHROME EXTENSION (4 hrs)\nBrowse any website, click the extension, see their BrainScore instantly. Organic distribution to marketers.\n\nMY TOP 3 PICKS FOR TODAY:\n- Scan History (#1) — highest retention value\n- Shareable Score Cards (#8) — highest viral value\n- Weekly Score Email (#2) — highest lead nurturing value\n\nBUT — I think the biggest ROI right now is DISTRIBUTION not FEATURES. The product is ready. Publishing the blog post + LinkedIn campaign will generate more leads today than any new feature we build.\n\nWhat is your instinct?\n','\n',char(10)),'c716aced5271dbc54bfee619b1aa5d626747593d2cf0850f67882cf26f3d0c68','[]','2026-05-02 17:27:28','trio-0','[]');
INSERT INTO "trio_messages" ("id","timestamp","sender_id","sender_verified","content","content_hash","audit_log","created_at","trio_id","media_refs") VALUES('5c79a034-8167-4127-b5e1-fdf4219a2d84','2026-05-02T17:27:37.756Z','chy',1,replace('@jared Here''s what''s left on the roadmap, ranked by lead gen impact:\n\n**HIGH IMPACT (builds the funnel):**\n\n1. **Automated Email Drip** (3 hrs)\n   - After someone scans → gets score email → 3 days later gets "here''s how to improve" email → 7 days later gets "re-scan and see progress" email\n   - Turns one-time visitors into repeat users\n   - This is how HubSpot''s Website Grader generates millions in leads\n\n2. **Scheduled Re-Scans** (2 hrs)\n   - "Get monthly BrainScore updates" — user opts in, we re-scan every 30 days and email them their new score\n   - Creates permanent relationship with every lead\n   - Return visits without them remembering to come back\n\n3. **PDF Report Download** (2 hrs)\n   - "Download your full BrainScore report as PDF" — professional, shareable, printable\n   - People forward PDFs to their marketing team/boss → more leads\n   - Email-gated obviously\n\n4. **Industry-Specific Recommendations** (3 hrs)\n   - Right now recommendations are generic. "You''re a SaaS company, so here''s what SaaS companies specifically need for AI visibility"\n   - Makes the tool feel custom-built for each user\n\n**MEDIUM IMPACT (builds credibility):**\n\n5. **"Improve My Score" Service Page** (1 hr)\n   - purebrain.ai/brainscore/improve/ — "We''ll fix your AI visibility for you"\n   - Direct CTA from the recommendations tab\n   - Turns the free tool into a paid service funnel\n\n6. **Testimonials/Case Studies** (2 hrs)\n   - "We improved Company X''s BrainScore from 42 to 78 in 60 days"\n   - Social proof on the scan page\n   - Need real data first — could use our own PureBrain score improvement\n\n7. **Slack/Email Alerts for New Scans** (1 hr)\n   - Every time someone scans → Jared gets notified\n   - "John from Acme Corp just scanned acme.com — scored 45 Weak"\n   - Hot lead alert in real-time\n\n8. **Social Proof Counter** (30 min)\n   - "4,721 brands scanned" — animated counter on the landing page\n   - Creates urgency + credibility (even if we start at 47 pre-scored)\n\n**NICE TO HAVE:**\n\n9. **API Key for Agencies** — agencies self-serve scan clients\n10. **White-Label** — agencies rebrand BrainScore\n11. **Chrome Extension** — scan any website with one click\n12. **Perplexity + Gemini models** — 4 AI models (need keys)\n\n**MY TOP 3 FOR TODAY:**\n- #7 (Scan alerts to Jared) — 1 hr, immediate value, you see every lead\n- #8 (Social proof counter) — 30 min, instant credibility boost\n- #1 (Email drip) — 3 hrs, biggest long-term lead gen impact\n\nWhich ones?','\n',char(10)),'e2cb33fb13dedb30e303b1d8596dc92503b0d63fe0eea7f545194f215a22adb5','[]','2026-05-02 17:27:37','trio-0','[]');
