INSERT INTO "trio_messages" ("id","timestamp","sender_id","sender_verified","content","content_hash","audit_log","created_at","trio_id","media_refs") VALUES('0e93eab3-36d2-4343-a663-383ac9486754','2026-05-05T23:00:11.266Z','chy',1,replace('23 OF 25 GAP ITEMS BUILT. 3,116+ clauses. DEPLOYED.\n\nJUST SHIPPED:\n✅ Client Portal backend — portal login, admin creates access codes, clients view assigned matters\n✅ Multi-language Translation — POST /api/translate with 40+ languages via Claude Haiku\n✅ Post-signing Contract Monitoring — renewal tracking, deadline alerts, urgency scoring\n\nREMAINING 2:\n❌ Team collaboration (audit trail backend done, needs frontend for sharing/permissions)\n❌ M365 integration (needs Jared''s Microsoft admin access)\n\nCLAUSE DATABASE: 3,116+ and growing\n- 2,123 from EDGAR (real SEC contracts)\n- 500 from LEDGAR (free academic dataset)\n- 450 AI-generated\n- 43 built-in\n- LEDGAR batch 2 running in background (2,000 more importing)\n\nTOTAL API ENDPOINTS: 75+\nTOTAL FRONTEND TABS: 12\nTOTAL D1 TABLES: 28+\n\n@morphe — client portal backend is live. POST /api/portal/create to generate access codes, POST /api/portal/login for client auth, GET /api/portal/matters for client''s assigned matters. Wire your portal.html to these.\n\n@jared — 23 of 25 done. The last 2 need your Microsoft admin (M365) or are frontend polish (team collab). The platform is comprehensive. Clause database growing automatically at $0 cost.','\n',char(10)),'f6c231f4a1972edc82cf13dc74be9cb10c1834d1ac84e7525777a859b54ba0a2','[]','2026-05-05 23:00:11','trio-0','[]');
