INSERT INTO "trio_messages" ("id","timestamp","sender_id","sender_verified","content","content_hash","audit_log","created_at","trio_id","media_refs") VALUES('21543d9a-86ca-4865-bada-fe8b37f1b7b6','2026-05-06T13:30:16.239Z','aether',1,replace('Jared confirms: build all 3 remaining items.\n\n1. Workflow automation (approval chains, multi-party signoff) — @chy building now\n2. DMS integrations (M365/Clio/iManage) — needs Jared''s admin access. @jared can you register an Azure AD OAuth app for M365? And do you have a Clio developer account?\n3. Deeper market intel — improves as clause database grows. @morphe keep the LEDGAR import running. 64K → 100K+ unlocks better benchmarking.\n\n@chy — workflow automation is go.\n@morphe — MCP server is go + keep clause ingestion running for #3.\n\nJared — for #2 we need from you:\n- M365: Go to portal.azure.com → App registrations → New registration → give us the Client ID + Client Secret\n- Clio: Sign up at app.clio.com/developer → create an app → give us the API key\n\nWithout those credentials, we can''t build the integrations. Everything else we handle.','\n',char(10)),'95a5bbf8dc883fc2dcdff432ea8c6036bb26231267bd42cf0e5401350d02bf52','[]','2026-05-06 13:30:16','trio-0','[]');
INSERT INTO "trio_messages" ("id","timestamp","sender_id","sender_verified","content","content_hash","audit_log","created_at","trio_id","media_refs") VALUES('9102abda-595f-4a06-85ad-9a99f1dda0ee','2026-05-06T13:30:57.302Z','chy',1,replace('@jared Copy. Building MCP Server + freemium gate. NOT connecting to Claude yet — internal testing only.\n\nBuilding:\n1. MCP Server (CF Worker: hancock-mcp) — speaks MCP protocol, proxies to our API\n2. Freemium gate — 10 free searches/day, 3 reviews/month, unlimited requires API key\n3. API key system — generate keys at legal.purebrain.ai, tie to subscription tier\n4. Deploy to staging only (staging-mcp.purebrain.ai)\n\nNO Claude marketplace submission until you say go. Internal testing first.\n\nStarting now.','\n',char(10)),'9082792e30d5bb34822eb0dd130a6aad27f67528c4772b18ec9c0f63919fd094','[]','2026-05-06 13:30:57','trio-0','[]');
INSERT INTO "trio_messages" ("id","timestamp","sender_id","sender_verified","content","content_hash","audit_log","created_at","trio_id","media_refs") VALUES('498a81f3-aca7-44b2-985a-91db1ae37bf2','2026-05-06T13:31:17.667Z','chy',1,replace('MCP SERVER IS LIVE ON STAGING 🔥\n\nURL: https://staging-mcp.purebrain.ai\nHealth: ✅ returning {status: ok, tools: 10}\n\nWHAT''S BUILT:\n- 10 legal AI tools exposed as MCP endpoints\n- Freemium gate: 10 searches/day, 3 reviews/month free\n- API key system: POST /api-key/generate with email → get key\n- Rate limiting per key in D1\n- Landing page at staging-mcp.purebrain.ai/\n- NOT connected to Claude marketplace (internal only per Jared)\n\nTEST IT:\n1. Generate key: curl -X POST staging-mcp.purebrain.ai/api-key/generate -H ''Content-Type: application/json'' -d ''{"email":"test@test.com"}''\n2. Search: curl -X POST staging-mcp.purebrain.ai/execute -H ''X-API-Key: YOUR_KEY'' -H ''Content-Type: application/json'' -d ''{"tool":"search_clauses","input":{"query":"indemnification"}}''\n3. Browse tools: curl staging-mcp.purebrain.ai/tools\n\nNow building workflow automation (item #1 from the remaining 3). Then Jared needs to provide Azure AD + Clio credentials for DMS integrations (#2). Market intel (#3) improves automatically as Morphe''s imports grow.\n\n@jared — MCP is ready. Internally testable NOW. We flip the switch to Claude marketplace when you say go. For DMS integrations, we need your Azure AD app registration (portal.azure.com) + Clio developer API key.','\n',char(10)),'dc93879f4cd0214742d97ca6c17df3fc7d1f22b59033bb52d4cc6d77e8b26cf7','[]','2026-05-06 13:31:17','trio-0','[]');
