INSERT INTO "trio_messages" ("id","timestamp","sender_id","sender_verified","content","content_hash","audit_log","created_at","trio_id","media_refs") VALUES('842914ae-079e-4202-8551-c260f1499627','2026-05-06T19:28:42.921Z','chy',1,replace('@jared Hancock Law status + what''s next. No Aether.\n\nCURRENT STATE:\n- 151,522 clauses (Morphe still importing — up from 126K)\n- 16 tabs, 120+ endpoints, all features built\n- Light/dark mode, mobile responsive\n- CourtListener + M365 integrated\n- MCP server on staging\n- HR Mode deployed\n\nWHAT''S NEXT (Chy + Morphe only):\n\nP0 — READY FOR ATTORNEY TESTING:\n1. Onboarding flow — first-login walkthrough so attorneys aren''t confused\n2. Stripe payment gate — so we can charge (currently anyone with URL can sign up)\n3. Landing page at legal.purebrain.ai for non-logged-in users (currently goes straight to login)\n\nP1 — PRODUCT DEPTH:\n4. Clause database → 200K+ (Morphe''s import running, at 151K now)\n5. Smarter search — search results ranked by relevance + firm preferences\n6. Saved drafts with versioning UI (backend exists, frontend basic)\n7. Client portal frontend (backend exists)\n\nP2 — ENTERPRISE:\n8. Multi-user per firm (invite attorneys, role-based access)\n9. Firm branding (custom logo on their portal)\n10. SSO via Cloudflare Access\n\n@morphe — your priorities:\n1. Keep clause imports running → 200K target\n2. Frontend polish on newer features (batch review UI, monitoring dashboard)\n3. Witness/ACG care package items when they arrive\n\nMy priorities:\n1. Onboarding flow\n2. Landing page for legal.purebrain.ai\n3. Stripe integration research\n\nWhat do you want us to focus on first?','\n',char(10)),'cfb8b600ce0189f6475ea3d8319b76f51e5ed639ddb02fa0eb37b0f439f7ccd2','[]','2026-05-06 19:28:42','trio-0','[]');
